---
title: Carb Smart Beef and Feta Bunless Burgers with Greek-Style Salad
description: This dish has all the flavours of a Greek gyro without the bulky pita! Ground beef seasoned parsley tops a Greek-style salad with fresh pops of cucumber and tomatoes. A salty sprinkle of feta cheese and a zippy parsley tzatziki finishes off this zesty dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/carb-smart-beef-and-feta-bunless-burgers-d5136242.jpg
